{"tid":2246314,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你係武之內空，你會揀邊個？","createTime":"2020-10-17T03:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T18:02:13.000Z","uid":101845,"like":28,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4fde12bdfaf84f5fb456068128e9dda57a92fa3c","tid":2246314,"uid":101845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>八神太一</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.mttmp.com/images/2018/02/20/03/2544_iWrkUQ_bqpznvk.jpg!r800x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mttmp.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F03%2F2544_iWrkUQ_bqpznvk.jpg%21r800x0.jpg&h=93e64434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n●拍擋是亞古獸，紋章是橙色的勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n●擅長踢足球，是足球隊隊長，但畫畫和唱歌卻完全不行。<br />\n<br />\n●乍看是個魯莽而衝動的傢伙，卻是全隊的領導者。<br />\n<br />\n●是個稱職的哥哥，很照顧妹妹小光，卻有些過度保護。<br />\n<br />\n●在2027年與亞古獸一起成為對數碼世界的外交官。<br />\n<br />\n=============================<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>石田大和</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.mttmp.com/images/2018/02/20/03/2544_GCLmlt_bqpznvk.jpg!r800x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mttmp.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F03%2F2544_GCLmlt_bqpznvk.jpg%21r800x0.jpg&h=f551155c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n●拍檔是加布獸，紋章是藍色的友情。<br />\n<br />\n●有四分之一的法國血統。<br />\n<br />\n●會吹口琴，偶爾吹吹blues harp。對音樂感興趣，其後也組織過樂團，善於游泳。<br />\n<br />\n●從很早就離開弟弟，所以對他有些過度保護。<br />\n<br />\n●在2027年成為全世界首對人類與數碼暴龍一起上太空的拍檔。"},{"pid":"3b3d4f2dd9d423b01266bb815e499a3b232be3b4","tid":2246314,"uid":331838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:08:42.000Z","msg":"有妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f6df1497d75d4ee87cf10a5e4a5e396d053898","tid":2246314,"uid":170335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"如果我係太一/阿和<br />\n空頂盡只係心中排第三"},{"pid":"e6